citation distribution for hep spires image hep hepnames institutions conferences experiments jobs videos citation distribution for hep created december 1 2005 asked by jan conrad answered by travis brooks this table consists of the histogram of citations for the entire database in other words it is the number and fraction of the database that falls into certain citation windows number of papers log scale citation bin 50 100 250 500 1000 absolute amount 26574 14683 3304 961 343 percent of total 11.31 6.25 1.41 0.41 0.15 data as of sat 4 sep 2010 when there were 234885 citeable papers in hep note that citeable papers are all journal and eprint articles for which we can track citations also note that the bins are not cumulative ie a paper with 512 citations is only counted in the 500 bin not in the 50 and 100 about spires slac slac library contact spires hep is a joint project of slac desy & fnal as well as the worldwide hep community mirrors desy germany fermilab us ihep russia durham u uk slac us yitp japan lipi indonesia last updated 12 08 2005 valid xhtml 1.0 valid css
